partman-crypto (2) UNRELEASED; urgency=low

  [ Max Vozeler ]
  * Add Depends on loop-aes-modules (provided by loop-aes-$KVERS-di)
  * Add check for separate /boot partition if the root partition 
    should be encrypted. Thanks to Riku Voipio.
  * Use debconf_select in crypto_dooption; Option values can now be
    translated if corresponding templates exist.

  [ Frans Pop ]
  * Old-style options for head/tail are no longer supported by new busybox.

